Quickstart
----------

  1. Install TurboGears >= 1.0.1
     (see http://www.turbogears.org/download/).
  2. Download `TGFastData 0.9.a7unofficial`_
     (unofficial version with patch to work with TG >= 1.x)
     and install with::
     
       [sudo] easy_install TGFastData-0.9a7unofficial-py2.4.egg

  3. Download_ the ${name} `source distribution`_.
  4. Unpack the archive ``${src_package_tbz}`` or
     ``${src_package_zip}``.
  5. Change into the created directory ``${package_name}``.
  6. Run ``./start-bookmarker.py``.
  7. Open your browser at ``http://localhost:8080/``.
  8. Click on ``bookmarks demo`` and...
  9. ... log in with username/password ``test``.

*Share & enjoy!*


